            <h2>Temporary Suspension of Delivery Center Status</h2>

            <p>It is with regret that we report that PNA&rsquo;s status as a delivery center for British Canoeing has been temporarily suspended, effective Dec. 18, 2017. This suspension came after a recent review by British Canoeing international of our progress over the past 18 months toward meeting all of the criteria necessary for being a British Canoeing delivery center. The current PNA board is diligently working to meet the goals needed to be reinstated as soon as possible.<br>
              <br>
              British Canoeing is fully committed to our regaining delivery center status, as are we. We will update you on our progress, but until then all of the following will have to go through British Canoeing International, not PNA:</p>

            <ul>
              <li>Course authorizations</li>
              <li>Learner Registrations</li>
              <li>Certifications</li>
            </ul>

            <p>PNA will be sending out a separate letter to all PNA Providers outlining this temporary policy.<br>
              <br>
              <strong>WHAT DOES THIS MEAN FOR YOU?</strong><br>
              If your PNA membership is expired, you can renew with PNA up until December 17, 2017 and British Canoeing will honor that membership through its expiration date. After that date you will have to <a href="https://mcd.britishcanoeing.org.uk/MCD/Online/Membership/Index?organisationId=1746&amp;layout=Online" target="_blank" style="color: #24b3e3;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: none;">join British Canoeing</a>.<br>
              <br>
              If you join British Canoeing during this suspension time, PNA will honor this membership and transfer you back to PNA when we regain our delivery center status.<br>
              <br>
              If you have questions or concerns, please contact our administrator, Scott Fairty, at <a href="mailto:info@paddlesportsnorthamerica.org?subject=Question%20about%20delivery%20center%20status" target="_blank" style="color: #24b3e3;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: none;">info@paddlesportsnorthamerica.org</a>.</p>
          </div>
