	    <h2>British Canoeing Coach Award (New Level 2)</h2>
	    <p>British Canoeing will launch its Coach Award in January 2018, replacing the Level 2 coach award, as well as rebrand the Level 1, 3 and 4 coaching awards. The restructured Coach Award has been designed to ensure current research is reflected as well as provide the learner with direct entry opportunities that are relevant to their discipline. British Canoeing has listened to the feedback received and reviews and, as such, we are replacing the portfolio and workbook requirements with interactive eLearning to support the learning and development of the coach.</p>
	    <p>The Coach Award will also encompass the existing Moderate Water and Advanced Water Endorsements, as well as competition coach pathways, providing consistency and standardization across all disciplines at this level.</p>
	    <p><a href="https://www.britishcanoeing.org.uk/courses/new-for-2018/#new-coaches" target="_blank">British Canoeing Announcement</a></p>
	  </div>

